Privacy Policy for Touring Bot 3.0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 Introduction\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa400\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Touring Bot 3.0 is a specialized data entry tool designed for the music industry, aimed at compiling information about specific artists or festivals into a structured table format for academic and research purposes. This privacy policy outlines our practices regarding the collection, use, and protection of personal information through our GPT and the associated API (trafilatura.p.rapidapi.com) used for content extraction.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Data Collection and Usage\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa400\partightenfactor0

